<p>Adding work packages to an iteration</p><p>Iterations can group work packages with the same due dates. 
  </p> 
	  
		<ul> 
		   
			  At least one iteration must
				exist. 
			  
		   
		 
	 </ul> 
	  
		<p> Group all work packages due for the
		  same milestone into one iteration. 
		</p> 
	  
	  
		 
		   In 
			 My Products, expand the desired product. 
		   
		 
		 
		  Click the desired release. 
		   
		 
		 
		  Click 
			 Iterations. 
		   
		 
		 
		  Select the box around the iteration to which the work package
			 belongs.
		   
		  
			 <p>Work packages that are not yet added to an iteration are shown in 
				Unscheduled.
			 
		  </p>
		   
			 <p>All work packages in the
				selected iteration appear. 
			 </p> 
		   
		 
		  Drag and drop the work package into the desired iteration. 
		   
		 
	  
		<p> The work package is now part of the
		  selected iteration. 
		</p> 
	  
  